   <Description>
            <p>Assigned OID: 2.16.840.1.113883.2.1.3.2.4.17.7</p>
            <p>Three types of Legitimate Relationship may be "manually" created by a user. These are contained within the LRType vocabulary. They are:</p>
            <ul>
               <li>Self-claimed</li>
               <li>Colleague granted</li>
               <li>Expressed patient consent to access.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>If any of the above LRType are selected then the user must select a AccessReasonCode from the list below. Please note that the list is constrained depending upon the LRType code.</p>
